  "title": "Senior / Project Planner/Planning Engineer",
  "description": "<h3>Project Planner/Planning Engineer</h3>\n<h3>Visit www.ourrecruiters.com</h3>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop and maintain project schedules.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and update project schedules.</li>\n  <li>Track and report progress against the plan.</li>\n  <li>Identify schedule deviations and suggest corrective actions.</li>\n  <li>Collect and evaluate data to monitor project schedules.</li>\n  <li>Monitor working budget, forecasting, and final costs.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with engineering, procurement, and project teams to review scope.</li>\n  <li>Prepare periodic project reports for management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor's Degree/Postgraduate Diploma in Engineering or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of experience in construction and engineering industries.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office, Microsoft Project, and Primavera P6.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Attention to detail and good time management.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in Primavera P6 is essential.</li>\n</ul>",
